Gymnasts are SuperheroesOriginally an ebook and DVD set, the curriculum has evolved into seminars and more than fifteen online courses, of which half have been published and the rest are in progress. Prior to GymnasticBodies, though, elite gymnastics remained completely isolated from the rest of society. Adults often assumed gymnasts who mastered ring strength, and other incredible feats were simply a lucky few who possessed 'the right stuff' to achieve such feats. In contrast to comic superheroes, they are built over time from ordinary people. They lacked the knowledge and training to take advantage of gymnastics' aesthetic and athletic potential. According to Coach Sommer, the âright stuffâ is not purely genetic, but rather a progressive, structured approach to fitness. A gymnastics program that bridges the lack of flexibility and strength of most adults with the possibilities of high-level gymnastics has adapted and scaled the conditioning that created hundreds of National, State, and Regional champions. With all these decades of expertise and success, you are uniquely positioned to benefit from them. To improve yourself, it is only necessary to work consistently.
